text: haey avei del puok anak( mnoussa lok) ban khvengkoumnit knea nouv brakear namuoy nowknong kechchakar sasanea damnaohsray robsa vea ku trauv vilotralb towkean a l laoh . noh haey ku a l laoh chea mcheasa robsakhnhom del khnhom brakl kar touk chetd champoh trong haey champoh trong temuoyokt del khnhom trauv vilotralb
